sequenceDiagram
  autonumber
  participant U as SOC Analyst
  participant UI as React UI
  participant API as FastAPI :8080
  participant WS as /ws/audit

  U->>UI: Open dashboard
  UI->>API: GET /healthz
  UI->>API: GET /api/v1/audit/stats
  UI->>API: GET /api/v1/audit/records?decision=block&limit=10
  UI->>API: GET /api/v1/agents
  API-->>UI: KPI + blocked rows + trust data
  UI-->>U: Render score, charts, recent blocks

  U->>UI: Navigate to Audit Log and enable Live
  UI->>API: GET /api/v1/audit/records?limit=50
  UI->>WS: Connect ws://localhost:8080/ws/audit
  WS-->>UI: New audit record events
  UI-->>U: Prepend animated rows + details

  U->>UI: Open policy versions and click Restore
  UI->>API: POST /api/v1/policies/{ns}/{class}/rollback
  API-->>UI: rollback confirmation
  UI-->>U: Updated version table state
